            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Elon Musk：决定自己用 xAI 做游戏，游戏产业被大企业箝制，</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/28/elon-musk-xai-make-game/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=elon-musk-xai-make-game</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/28/elon-musk-xai-make-game/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 07:00:46 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Elon Musk]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Twitter]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[x]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[狗狗币]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1277590</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>狗狗币开发者在 X （前称 Twitter）发文指控游戏产业被意识形态控制。帖文引来 Elon Musk 回应，扬言要利用旗下 AI 公司 xAI 开发游戏，以「拨乱反正」。</p><p>昨日（27 日）狗狗币开发者 @BillyM2k 在 X 发文，表示目前游戏产业（游戏开发商、游戏新闻业界）为何如此着重意识形态，并表示认为游戏玩家一直是喜欢开玩笑、反霸权、不喜欢意识形态操控的人，不理解玩家们为甚么要妥协于目前游戏产业「外行人控制内行人」之状况。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">i don&#8217;t understand how game developers and game journalism got so ideologically captured</p><p>gamers have always been trolls, anti-greedy corporations, anti-bs</p><p>gamers have always rejected dumb manipulative bs, and can tell when someone is an outsider poser</p><p>why lean into the bs?</p><p>— Shibetoshi Nakamoto (@BillyM2k) <a href="https://twitter.com/BillyM2k/status/1861800506567643401?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 27, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>@Billy2M2k 帖文引起 Elon Musk 共鸣，并回复表示目前游戏产业被大企业操控，因而造成以上情况。对此，Elon Musk 指会善用旗下 AI 开发公司 xAI 资源开发游戏，拨乱反正，令游戏回复以往好玩程度。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Too many game studios that are owned by massive corporations. <a href="https://twitter.com/xai?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@xAI</a> is going to start an AI game studio to make games great again! <a href="https://t.co/UR4nFODyfd">https://t.co/UR4nFODyfd</a></p><p>— Elon Musk (@elonmusk) <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1861801046949191686?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 27, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/images/story/2024/05/06/Elon-Musk-videogames.png?optimize=medium&amp;dpr=1.25&amp;auto=webp&amp;width=3840">Benzinga</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://x.com/elonmusk/status/1861801046949191686">elonmusk@X</a>、<a href="https://x.com/BillyM2k/status/1861800506567643401">BillyM2k@X</a><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
